									<ol class="list-group " >
											<li>Agile Values and Principles with FAIL FAST, INSPECT and ADAPT, LESS is MORE, SERVANT LEADER</li>
											<li>Dedicated and Empowered Product Owner – clear about Outcomes</li>
											<li>Iterative way with potentially shippable product for every Sprint (2-4 weeks)</li>
											<li>User Stories granular enough for E2E development and delivery</li>
											<li>Self-organizing teams, Cross-functional and Dedicated</li>
											<li>Servant leadership – Scrum Master</li>
											<li>Agile Ceremonies -  Communication and Collaboration, Visual progress</li>
											<li>Dependency Management</li>
									</ol>
